	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Gameobjectives 
	" Game objectives
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Emulator used: BizHawk 2.1.0
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Beats the game as fast as possible
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" BIOS: JPN 2.1
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 id=Comments 
	" Comments
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"This game is pretty simple, run right and hit the boss as fast as possible. I mainly improved the last boss fight with a better attack pattern by jumping at the beginning.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Other timing differences are due to loading times.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"I decided to improve this run mainly because of a silly bug in the original, where on vertical scrolling sections, the entire screen scrolls, along with your status box. This is an obvious emulation bug, so I wanted to have a fixed version.
	$LF
]div
